diagnostics are approximate.}
\item{NLS}{Nonlinear least squares on the original scale
\eqn{m_i = N_i^{\alpha} (\gamma + n_i/N_i)^{\beta} + \varepsilon_i}{m_i = N_i^alpha * (gamma + n_i/N_i)^beta + epsilon_i}.
